OL,7,FThere are signs of hope for as the
OL,8,Fnumber of people visiting Wales' high
OL,9,Fstreets has increased for the first
OL,10,Ftime in 12 months.
OL,12,FFigures from the Welsh Retail
OL,13,FConsortium suggest retailers were
OL,14,Fhelped by the early Easter bank
OL,15,Fholiday.
OL,17,FThe new data reveals Welsh retail
OL,18,Ffootfall increased by 0.4% in March.
OL,19,FThis is up from -8.0% in February.
