OL,7,FIt comes as, after multiple delays, a
OL,8,Fnew market modelled after a shipping
OL,9,Fcontainer has opened in .
OL,11,FFfos Caerffili opened its doors on
OL,12,FFriday 5 April, after being previously
OL,13,Fdelayed four times.
OL,15,FThe most recent postponement occurred
OL,16,Fon 15 March after days of intense rain
OL,17,Fcaused the finishing touches to be
OL,18,Fdelayed.
