OL,7,FSam Eastcott is the owner of The
OL,8,FCircular Studio which is trading at
OL,9,FFfos Caerffili. She believes the
OL,10,Fmarket is helping to provide
OL,11,Fopportunities to link up with other
OL,12,Flocal traders.
OL,14,FShe believes: "I didn't know any of
OL,15,Fthem two, three weeks ago."
OL,17,F"Now like we've been able to support
OL,18,Feach other or even talk about
OL,19,Fcollaborations which is something
OL,20,Fcompletely unbeknown to me.
