OL,7,F"So it's been amazing to actually
OL,8,Fthink about that as a new possibility."
OL,10,FIn a post on social media, the Ffos
OL,11,FCaerffili team said: ", you've been so
OL,12,Fpatient. Diolch. We're very happy to
OL,13,Fannounce that Ffos Caerffili will be
OL,14,Fofficially opening on Friday 5th April
OL,15,Ffrom 9am.
OL,17,F"Come down for coffee, brunch, plants,
OL,18,Ffish, vintage clothes, dog treats, and
OL,19,Fso much more. We can't wait to see you
OL,20,Fthere."
