OL,7,FShe added: "It's just lovely to see
OL,8,Flocal people supporting something, and
OL,9,Factually to support something from the
OL,10,Fget-go and to be apart of the history
OL,11,Fof Caerphilly really - something
OL,12,Fcompletely different."
OL,14,FThe community market aims to serve as
OL,15,Fa hub for the town and is an integral
OL,16,Fcomponent of the Town 2035 Placemaking
OL,17,FPlan, which has received financial
OL,18,Fbacking from the Welsh Government's
OL,19,FTransforming Towns initiative.
