OL,7,FAccording to Jamie Pritchard, deputy
OL,8,Fleader of Council, Ffos is expected to
OL,9,Fhouse 28 independent retailers, such
OL,10,Fas Taiwanese street food vendor Bao
OL,11,FSelecta and vintage clothing store
OL,12,FCircular Studio. It also aims to
OL,13,Fcreate between 40 and 50 new jobs in
OL,14,Fthe community.
OL,16,FMr Pritchard said: "Ffos Caerffili has
OL,17,Fencountered a number of challenges,
OL,18,Fwhich have now been overcome. The
OL,19,Ffacility is nearly ready to open and
OL,20,Fthere is a real sense of anticipation
OL,21,Fin the town.
