OL,7,F"We are creating a venue where
OL,8,Fbusinesses can thrive, right in the
OL,9,Fheart of the town centre. Promoting
OL,10,Fand developing new business
OL,11,Fopportunities is absolutely critical
OL,12,Fand we're looking forward to opening
OL,13,Fthe doors."
OL,15,FThe project has received backing from
OL,16,Fthe European Regional Development Fund
OL,17,Fvia the Welsh Government, as well as
OL,18,Fthe UK Shared Prosperity Fund.
